main event: A project Blue Book document dated July 24, 1952, regarding an unknown object observed at Biggs AFB, Texas.
interesting points: The document is part of File 1586 from 1952., The report includes one photograph showing a landscape with clouds and mountains., The photograph features a label indicating 'BASE 6,000''., A compass rose is present at the bottom of the image., The designated location of the 'Hover' was marked with an 'X'.
